A special importance is attached to the numerous initiatives to become more directly aware of the school framework of young people who feed the world of work.
It is our duty to focus attention on this phenomenon and not to divert attention from its social seriousness. One must put a legislative standard into effect and improve it.
On the other hand, the President of the Chamber of Gianfranco Fini stressed "like the phenomenon of work-related deaths constitutes an urgent social emergency, which offends the conscience of all of us and forces all institutions to work towards decisive rules that aim to put an end to the problem".
