Mercandelli also spoke about "the progressive deterioration of protection for victims of accidents at work" and addressed the "disposal of the social system against which we have been fighting in recent years".
"The aim, therefore, is to return a guarantee to the worker in order to ensure that the victim's fate of an accident at work does not depend on voluntary or accidental donations, which are decided by a legislator on time."
