Brussels had commissioned the independent scientific committee in view of the widespread use of portable musical instruments among young people.
"The scientists - thus closing the EU communication - confirm that we are quite concerned and that the European Commission, together with the other members of the European Union and those concerned, will now examine the necessary measures to better protect children and young people from the noise coming from portable music devices and similar devices."
